#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:141
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Chex Quest (1996) was the first video game included as a prize in cereal boxes, and it's playable right here."
msgstr "Chex Quest (1996年)是第一部作爲獎項列入穀物盒的電子遊戲,可以在這裏玩."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_chex_quest.html.heex:84
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Chex Quest was the first video game ever included as a prize in cereal boxes, shipped with 5.7 million boxes. Sales of Chex cereal jumped over 200% during the promotion."
msgstr "Chex Quest是有史以來第一個作爲獎品列入穀類盒的電子遊戲,以570萬箱的運貨. 在推廣期間,Chex穀物的銷售額超過了200%。"

