#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake_shareware.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Nine Inch Nails frontman Trent Reznor created the sound effects and ambient music — the nail ammunition boxes even feature the NIN logo. Quake was id Software's first fully 3D engine, a massive technical leap beyond DOOM's 2.5D rendering. The shareware edition was the sixth-best-selling computer game of 1996. It runs on the QuakeSpasm engine compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "九寸釘前鋒特倫特·雷茲諾創造了音效和環境音樂——指甲彈藥箱甚至有NIN標誌的特色. Quake是id Software的第一個全3D引擎,是超越DOOM2.5D渲染的大規模技術飛躍. 共享軟件版是1996年第六暢銷電腦遊戲. 它運行在編譯到WebAssembly的QuakeSpasm引擎上."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_fotaq.html.heex:66
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Opens up after crash"
msgstr "崩潰後打開"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife_uplink.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Originally distributed as a free standalone disc in retail outlets. In November 2023, Uplink was bundled with Half-Life as part of the 25th Anniversary Update, making it officially available on Steam for the first time. This runs on Xash3D-FWGS (GoldSource reimplementation) compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "最初作爲自由獨立碟在零售點發行. 2023年11月,Uplink與\"半條命\"捆綁,作爲\"25週年更新\"的一部分,首次在Steam上正式發佈. 這運行在編譯到WebAssembly的Xash3D-FWGS(黃金源重執行)上."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedm.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Originally maintained by Jim \"Rellik\" McDougald, FreeDM has undergone major overhauls with new levels replacing weaker ones. The maps feature Aquatex and Egyptian texture sets and work in single-player as exploration arenas. It runs on the PrBoom+ engine compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "最初由Jim \"Rellik\" McDougald維護,FreeDM經歷了大修,新的關卡取代了較弱的關卡. 地圖以Aquatex和埃及紋理集爲特色,在單人遊戲中作爲探索競技場工作. 它運行在編譯爲WebAssembly的PrBoom+引擎上."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedoom2.html.heex:76
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "PWAD compatible"
msgstr "PWAD 兼容"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:138
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Pending sessions expire in 5 minutes. The lobby expires after 15 minutes of inactivity (with a warning at 10 minutes)."
msgstr "5分鐘後卸任。 大廳在15分鐘無活動後失效(警告時間爲10分鐘)."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedoom1.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Phase 1 replaces Ultimate DOOM with 4 episodes of 9 levels each (36 total). Enemy designs differ from the originals but fulfill the same gameplay roles. The project remains under active development and is compatible with most classic DOOM WAD mods. It runs on the PrBoom+ engine compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "第1階段用4集,每集9個關卡(共36個關卡)取代最終DOOM. 敵人設計與原作不同,但完成了相同的遊戲角色. 該項目仍在積極開發中,與大多數經典的DOOM WAD Mods兼容. 它運行在編譯爲WebAssembly的PrBoom+引擎上."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedoom2.html.heex:93
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Phase 2 is compatible with DOOM II and Final Doom PWADs, giving you access to over 30 years of community-created content — thousands of level packs, total conversions, and gameplay mods."
msgstr "第二階段與DOOM II和 Final Doom PWADs兼容,允許您訪問超過30年的社區創建內容——數千個關卡包,總轉換,以及遊戲遊戲模式."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Play DOOM-engine games in your browser via WebAssembly. Seven game data options are available — from the original shareware to open-source replacements and total conversions."
msgstr "在您的瀏覽器中通過 WebAssembly 播放 DOOM 引擎遊戲 。 有七個遊戲數據選項——從最初的共享軟件到開源替換和總轉換."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Play Half-Life: Uplink in your browser via WebAssembly. The official 1999 Valve demo with 3 unique missions not found in the full game."
msgstr "通過WebAssembly在瀏覽器中播放\"半條命:向上鏈接\". 1999年Valve官方演示,包含3個在全遊戲中找不到的獨特任務."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Play Quake-engine games in your browser via WebAssembly. Two game data options are available — the original shareware and the open-source LibreQuake."
msgstr "通過WebAssembly在瀏覽器中播放Quake-engine遊戲. 有兩個遊戲數據選項——原始共享軟件和開源LibreQuake."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Play Wolfenstein 3D in your browser via WebAssembly. The original 1992 shareware episode — 10 levels of the game that launched the first-person shooter genre."
msgstr "通過 Web Assembly 在您的瀏覽器中播放 Wolfenstein 3D 。 1992年最初的共享軟件集——推出第一人稱射擊流派的遊戲的10個關卡."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Play classic point & click adventures in your browser via WebAssembly. ScummVM powers freeware games from the golden age of adventure gaming (1992–1996)."
msgstr "通過WebAssembly在瀏覽器中播放經典點並點擊冒險. ScumVM從冒險遊戲的黃金時代(1992–1996)開始,賦予自由軟件遊戲權力."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Play the Quake II demo in your browser via WebAssembly. The official shareware demo includes Unit 1 of the singleplayer campaign."
msgstr "通過WebAssembly在瀏覽器中播放Quake II演示. 官方共享軟件演示包括單玩家運動的單元1."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_drascula.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Poor distribution by publisher DMM prevented many players from discovering the game at release. In 2008, Alcachofa Soft handed the source code to the ScummVM team, which added native support. It was re-released as freeware with subtitles in English, Spanish, German, French, and Italian. This is the full version with MP3 voice acting, running on ScummVM compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "出版商DMM發行不佳,使得許多玩家無法在發行時發現遊戲. 2008年,Alcachofa Soft將源代碼交給了渣滓VM團隊,該團隊增加了本土支持. 它作爲免費軟件重新發行,配有英文、西班牙文、德文、法文和意大利文字幕。 這是由 MP3 語音代理的完整版本, 運行在 ScummVM 上編譯爲 Web Assembly 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_drascula.html.heex:84
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Poor distribution by publisher DMM prevented many players from discovering the game. Despite this, HobbyConsolas declared it one of the nine best Spanish graphic adventure games in 2017."
