#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The original Episode 1 shareware (10 levels). The grandfather of FPS games, created by id Software. Freely redistributable."
msgstr "——原第1集共享軟件(10級). FPS遊戲的祖父,由id Software創建. 自由再分配。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake.html.heex:14
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The original Episode 1 shareware (1996). Full 3D FPS with Lovecraftian horrors. Freely redistributable."
msgstr "——原第1集共享軟件(1996). 3D FPS全裝Lovecraftian恐怖. 自由再分配。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:14
